node.text:
FOLLOW @ThaiSelectUSA & @losangeles_eats and TAG a friend you’d like to do a SPICY CHALLENGE WITH for a chance to win $100 toward your favorite Thai Restaurant (your choice)! 🌶🙌🏼 Winner will be chosen 2 weeks from now. 

In this video we joined the @emporiumthai family as they sampled 5 Thai dishes at different spice levels to see if they could handle the heat! 💥

What spice level can YOU handle?! 👅 #ad #ThaiSelectUSA 

Dishes in video: COCO MANGO SALAD 🥥🥭, THAI CRAB OMELETTE 🦀🍳, PHUKET WINGS 🍖, THAI BASIL 🌱🌶 and SEAFOOD DRUNKEN NOODLES 🍤☄️

CONGRATS @linaabopeep ! You’re the winner of this giveaway! Please DM me to claim prize!

📍6161 Sepulveda Blvd Van Nuys Ca 91411 (in front of ATT across from Costco)

node.text: Gold’n Kiss has NUTELLA inside the Chimney Cake, ice cream is coated in edible 24K Gold & topped w/ Ferrero Rocher! 💰👑 Matcha is topped w/ matcha powder, matcha Kit Kat, matcha Pandas & mint chocolate! 🍵🍫 Birthday Cake has Nutella inside the Chimney, Oreos, rainbow sprinkles, raspberry sauce & giant marshmallow! 🌈🔥 Address: 6771 Hollywood Blvd, Los Angeles, CA 90028 [WATCH INSTASTORY TO SEE MORE!]

node.text:
GRAND OPENING of @teaspoonlife is TOMORROW Saturday 8/7! 🥳💦 First 💯 customers get a FREE DRINK in a glass bottle (doors open @ NOON)! 🙌🏼 
BOGO drinks from 8/7-8/15 all day! (Buy 1 get 1 free only for in-store purchases.) 🧋🧋

They’ll also be giving away a MacBook Pro, AirPod Max & $50 Gift Cards if you enter their giveaway on their website http://teaspoonlife.com/giveaway 💻💸

Drinks in this pic: FLAMINGO w/ fresh Watermelon & Passionfruit juice 🦩🍉 and GRASSHOPPER w/ fresh cucumber juice and lychee green tea! 🥒🍵

📍 1947 Sawtelle Blvd, Unit E, Los Angeles, CA 90025
